I"<p>이전 포스트에서 예고한 말풍선 각주의 너비 오버플로우 문제를 픽스했습니다.</p>

<div class="language-js highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kd">let</span> <span class="nx">right</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">offset</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">left</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="nx">dialogFootnote</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">outerWidth</span><span class="p">();</span>

<span class="kd">let</span> <span class="nx">viewportWidth</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">document</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">documentElement</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">clientWidth</span> <span class="o">||</span> <span class="nb">window</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">innerWidth</span><span class="p">;</span>

<span class="k">if</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">right</span> <span class="o">&gt;</span> <span class="nx">viewportWidth</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="nx">offset</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">left</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">Math</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">max</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nx">offset</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">left</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">offset</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">left</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="nx">dialogFootnote</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">outerWidth</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="nx">viewportWidth</span><span class="p">));</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>위와 같은 코드를 삽입함으로써 이제 정상 작동하게 됐습니다.</p>

<p>물론, 누군가가 말풍선의 최소 너비를 미친듯이 늘린다면 여전히 오버플로우가 되겠으나, 저는 그럴 일이 없으므로 이대로 커밋합니다.</p>

